{
  "texts": [
    "Throughout the execution of a complex task, the LLM learns to answer questions grounded on the plan (L QA).",
    "• Open Requests.",
    "Often, a plan has an element that users wish to change or they are curious about, e.g., replace an ingredient or get a fun fact about it.",
    "This requires a learning objective L Open that captures what pieces of a plan can be used (and how) to match the user request.",
    "• Conversational Norms."
  ]
}